# Yellow Bank GenAI Agent – Architecture

User  
→ Yellow.ai GenAI Agent  
→ OTP API (Beeceptor)  
→ Loan Accounts API (Beeceptor)  
→ Loan Details API (Beeceptor)  
→ CSAT Feedback Agent  

Token Optimization Layer:
A projection step filters raw API responses and forwards only necessary fields to the LLM.
